Package javascript.swing.plaf

Class LookAndFeel

  • java.lang.Object
    • javascript.swing.plaf.LookAndFeel
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BootstrapLookAndFeel
    public abstract class LookAndFeel
extends java.lang.Object
    The abstract object of any implementation able to redefine the look and feel of all components. It is mandatory to set a Look&Feel before the creation of the first component; the default Look&Feel is the BootstrapLookAndFeel which can be set in this way LookAndFeel.CURRENT = BootstrapLookAndFeel.create()
    Author:
    gianpiero.diblasi
